description: The Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber Skin Protector is the clear choice for maximum scratch protection. The Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber Skin Protector goes beyond your traditional Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber screen protectors, skins, covers, and cases. TechSkin is made from the same film material used to protect luxury cars, military aircrafts, and NASA space shuttles. The Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber Skin Protector is custom made to specifically fit the Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber. Carry and protect your Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player with style!Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber Skin Protector Features: • Dry application for Carbon Fiber Skin • Includes Skinomi Screen Protector • Tough protective Carbon Fiber textured skin • Virtually indestructible skin protector • Preserves your Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player's original design • Protects your Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player from scratches, dents, and physical wear-and-tear • Provides protection without affecting the functions of your Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player • Non-sticky or restrictive outer surface Included: • Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Carbon Fiber Skin Protector • Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Screen Protector • 1 Bottle of Application Solution (for screen protector) • Installation Instructions • Lifetime Warranty Compatible with:Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 PlayerThe Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player Screen Protector features two layers of protection. The first, topmost layer contains no unsightly "orange peel effect," while providing scratch-resistance and UV protection for anti-yellowing. The second layer is a thick, puncture resistant film to minimize damage from scrapes and dents. Unlike other Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player screen protectors and skins, the TechSkin features "self-healing" technology, meaning scratches do not stay on the film, and keeps your Samsung Galaxy 5.0 Android Mp3 Player looking new.For installation instructions and video please see: TechSkin Installation Instructions*Lifetime Warranty for this product is offered by Skinomi.com, please contact Skinomi or review the FAQ section for more information regarding the warranty policy.WARNING: As with any electronic device, exposing it to excessive water or other fluids may cause harm to the device.
